{"tid":2088353,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"何以　情色王　水再笠","createTime":"2020-07-01T05:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T12:11:13.000Z","uid":3204,"like":14,"dislike":134,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"051d48a50c8dd91816ad6ce5464f433b62135ad2","tid":2088353,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T05:53:14.000Z","msg":"何以　情色王　水再笠<br />\n何以　令肉酸　亦恥笑<br />\n昂首　拒隻dup　道歉聲　響透<br />\n盼和平　歸於　瑞和<br />\n<br />\n何以　這污名　抹不走<br />\n何以　為安全　一世笠水<br />\n何解　宇城飛　練開打拳　好勁<br />\n我笠水　恕我　軟弱<br />\n<br />\n在瑞和　墜落　徬徨波台<br />\n迷霧裡　最遠處吹來　恥笑聲<br />\n我笠了　來齊集這裡　來全力退後<br />\n無膽　智慧　我be water<br />\n<br />\n宇清來到　要光復　這瑞和<br />\n世界情色　為條命　時代笠水<br />\n祈求　生存與笠水 萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮清勿小氣"},{"pid":"55ec929b490a653fcfcf8522fb73b3ed5150a7a7","tid":2088353,"uid":4156,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"a660fd8d9f24f8ffb2f8746aa919a5e4e114f269","tid":2088353,"uid":66357,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"死熱狗我屌柒你"},{"pid":"1d2a708a08010bdaa26fed280c09ff7748337481","tid":2088353,"uid":212835,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"睇開d啦，返第二間教會啦"},{"pid":"f27d95c8dbceaee645b4d82208cfc7935b52c7de","tid":2088353,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a660fd8d9f24f8ffb2f8746aa919a5e4e114f269","tid":2088353,"uid":66357,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"死熱狗我屌柒你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T05:55:52.000Z","msg":"應該西米發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f7961ab0c6e41236bfc46f39bc4918dd3ee81a","tid":2088353,"uid":196719,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T05:56:34.000Z","msg":"完全唔啱音<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"0b4086176356a5993466254656a8ca398bd31100","tid":2088353,"uid":66357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f27d95c8dbceaee645b4d82208cfc7935b52c7de","ti